The '''Museum of Technology, Helsinki''', is situated in [[Helsinki]], [[Finland]]. It is the only general [[technology museum|museum of technology]] in the country.<ref name="info" />

The Museum of Technology is operated by the private Museum of Technology Foundation which was established in 1969.<ref name="museo" /> The foundation was established by industrial and engineering organizations, museum professionals and the municipalities of the Helsinki metropolitan area.<ref name="museo" />

